{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">McShay Weapon Pack 4</h2>Gemma McShay has delivered time and time again, this latest Weapon Pack is no different. In this pack we\u2019re getting 3 brand new weapons, each bringing their own unique thing, mods and Exclusive Set.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The Deimos shotgun is a highly versatile option for any shotgun enthusiast, the Deimos allows you to choose between a high-power pump action setting and a high rate of fire automatic setting. <br>The Deimos comes with 9 unique weapon mods, and an Exclusive Set.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353510/extras/Shotgun_2.gif?t=1727954817\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The Amaroq 900 is a high-power sniper rifle excelling at long range, modeled after one of the most famous sniper rifles in all of gaming. <br>Sure to make you a terror of the battlefield, the Amaroq 900 comes with 12 unique mods, 1 mod compatible with other sniper rifles and 2 Exclusive Sets.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353510/extras/Sniper_2.gif?t=1727954817\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The Campbell 74 LMG is capable of putting a lot of fire down range, literally and figuratively! Not only does it have a tremendous rate of fire, but also comes with an actual underbarrel flamethrower! <br>The Campbell 74 comes with 7 unique mods and an Exclusive Set.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353510/extras/LMG_7.gif?t=1727954817\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353510/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727954817","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353510/page.bg.jpg?t=1727954817","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353510/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=17279548